# API-FREE PILOT IMPLEMENTATION

**Goal:** Pilot with one class of RAs and one RD before presenting to institution for scaling.

## Why API-Free?

| Approach | Cost | Complexity | Suitable For |
|----------|------|------------|--------------|
| Full API (Twilio + AWS) | $100-500/mo | High (developer needed) | Institution-wide |
| **API-Free Pilot** | **$0-50/mo** | **Low (no-code)** | **1 RD + 10 RAs** |

## Recommended Tech Stack (Zero Cost)

```
