## Dual-Purpose Data Flow

```
                           ACTIVITIES DATA
                                 â”‚
           â”Œâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”´â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”
           â”‚                                           â”‚
           â–¼                                           â–¼
    TOPOLOGY ENGINE                           ENGAGEMENT INDEX
    (Creates graph edges)                     (Predicts outcomes)
           â”‚                                           â”‚
           â”‚  Shared class    = +2.0 edge              â”‚  Breadth score (count)
           â”‚  Shared activity = +1.5 edge              â”‚  Depth (hours)
           â”‚  Shared interest = +1.0 edge              â”‚  Leadership (role)
           â”‚  Same study spot = +0.5 edge              â”‚  Satisfaction
           â”‚                                           â”‚  Barriers identified
           â”‚                                           â”‚
           â–¼                                           â–¼
    COMMUNITY STRUCTURE                       INDIVIDUAL RISK FLAGS
    (Î²â‚€, Î²â‚, bridges)                        (Under-engaged, isolated)
           â”‚                                           â”‚
           â””â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”¬â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”˜
