# APPENDIX: GOOGLE SHEETS TEMPLATE

## Tab Structure

| Tab Name | Purpose | Auto/Manual |
|----------|---------|-------------|
| `Raw Responses` | Form submission data | Auto (linked to Form) |
| `Scored Data` | Calculated scores + flags | Auto (formulas) |
| `Individual View` | Per-resident detail lookup | Manual lookup |
| `Floor Dashboard` | Aggregate metrics + charts | Auto (pivot tables) |
| `Trends` | Longitudinal analysis | Auto (charts) |
| `Activity Edges` | Connection matrix | Semi-auto |
| `Alert Log` | Record of follow-ups | Manual entry |

## Key Formulas

```
// PHQ-2 Score (assuming columns C & D have Q2 & Q3 responses)
=IF(C2="Not at all",0,IF(C2="Several days",1,IF(C2="More than half",2,3)))
  + IF(D2="Not at all",0,IF(D2="Several days",1,IF(D2="More than half",2,3)))

// UCLA-3 Score (columns H, I, J for Q8-Q10)
=IF(H2="Hardly ever",1,IF(H2="Some of the time",2,3))
  + IF(I2="Hardly ever",1,IF(I2="Some of the time",2,3))
  + IF(J2="Hardly ever",1,IF(J2="Some of the time",2,3))

// Belonging Mean (columns K, L, M for Q11-Q13, assuming 1-5 numeric)
=AVERAGE(K2:M2)

// Depression Flag
=IF(PHQ2_cell>=3, "ðŸŸ¡ DEP", "")

// Urgent Flag
=IF(PHQ2_cell>=5, "ðŸ”´ URGENT", IF(AND(PHQ2_cell>=3, UCLA3_cell>=7), "ðŸŸ  CONCERN", ""))

// Wellbeing Index (simplified)
=ROUND(100 * (1 - PHQ2/6*0.2 - GAD2/6*0.15 - (UCLA3-3)/6*0.2 - (5-Belong)/4*0.15 - (5-Week)/4*0.1 - (5-Sleep)/4*0.1 - (10-LifeSat)/10*0.1))

// Floor Average
=AVERAGEIF(Floor_column, "3E", Index_column)

// Conditional Formatting Rule (for row highlighting)
Custom formula: =REGEXMATCH($FLAGS_COLUMN, "ðŸ”´")  â†’ Red background
Custom formula: =REGEXMATCH($FLAGS_COLUMN, "ðŸŸ ")  â†’ Orange background
Custom formula: =REGEXMATCH($FLAGS_COLUMN, "ðŸŸ¡")  â†’ Yellow background
```
